sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Administrator
    participant FE as React<br/>AdminAuditPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>AuditLogListView
    participant SER as AuditLogSerializer
    participant Perm as IsAdmin
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    A->>FE: Navigate to Audit Logs page
    FE->>API: GET /api/audit/logs/
    API->>Perm: has_permission(request)
    Perm-->>API: Allowed (Admin role)
    API->>DB: AuditLog.objects.all().order_by("-timestamp")
    DB-->>API: QuerySet[AuditLog]
    API->>SER: AuditLogSerializer(logs, many=True)
    SER-->>API: Serialized audit entries
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {logs: [{action, admin, target, timestamp}, ...]}
    FE->>FE: getActionColor(action) for styling
    FE-->>U: Display immutable audit log table with action badges
